        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Which of the following is not a correct way to recover health?\\n\\n#L0##bSit on a chair.#l\\n#L1#Use a potion like #t2000000#.#l\\n#L2#Stand still without moving.#l\\n#L3#Sleep.#k#l"
